Edit 'BMP180.dev';
Prefix 'U';
Description '\
BOSCH BMP180 DIGITAL BAROMETRIC PRESSURE SENSOR<p>\n\
\n\
Web page: <a href="http://www.bosch-sensortec.com/en/homepage/products_3/environmental_sensors_1/bmp180_1/bmp180">http://www.bosch-sensortec.com/en/homepage/products_3/environmental_sensors_1/bmp180_1/bmp180</a><br>\n\
Datasheet: <a href="http://ae-bst.resource.bosch.com/media/products/dokumente/bmp180/BST-BMP180-DS000-09.pdf"> http://ae-bst.resource.bosch.com/media/products/dokumente/bmp180/BST-BMP180-DS000-09.pdf</a><p>\n\
\n\
The BMP180 is the function compatible successor of the BMP085, a new generation of high\n\
precision digital pressure sensors for consumer applications.<p>\n\
The ultra-low power, low voltage electronics of the BMP180 is optimized for use in mobile phones,\n\
PDAs, GPS navigation devices and outdoor equipment. With a low altitude noise of merely 0.25m at\n\
fast conversion time, the BMP180 offers superior performance. The I2C interface allows for easy\n\
system integration with a microcontroller.<p>\n\
The BMP180 is based on piezo-resistive technology for EMC robustness, high accuracy and linearity as\n\
well as long term stability.<p>\n\
\n\
Key features:<p>\n\
\n\
- Temperature measurement included<br>\n\
- I2C interface<br>\n\
- Fully calibrated<br>\n\
- Pb-free, halogen-free and RoHS compliant,<br>\n\
- MSL 1<p>\n\
\n\
Basic specs:<p>\n\
\n\
Pressure range: 300 to 1100hPa (+9000m to -500m relating to sea level)<br>\n\
Supply voltage: 1.8 to 3.6V (VDD), 1.62V to 3.6V (VDDIO)<br>\n\
Package: LGA package with metal lid<br>\n\
Small footprint: 3.6mm x 3.8mm<br>\n\
Super-flat: 0.93mm height<br>\n\
Low power: 5?A at 1 sample / sec. in standard mode<br>\n\
Low noise: 0.06hPa (0.5m) in ultra low power mode, 0.02hPa (0.17m) advanced resolution mode<p>\n\
\n\
Typical applications:<p>\n\
\n\
- Enhancement of GPS navigation (dead-reckoning, slope detection, etc.)<br>\n\
- In- and out-door navigation<br>\n\
- Leisure and sports<br>\n\
- Weather forecast<br>\n\
- Vertical velocity indication (rise/sink speed) <a href="https://pricing.snapeda.com/parts/BMP180/Bosch%20Sensortec/view-part?ref=eda">Check availability</a>';
