Edit 'USB-MICRO-001G.dev';
Prefix 'USB';
Description '\
<b>Seeed SKU 320010000 - SMD Micro USB-B-W/P\n\
<br><br>\n\
MPN: ST-USB-001G - Updated Dave Williams\n\
<br>\n\
<br>\n\
Important Notes:\n\
</b><br>\n\
This part requires milling slots. Please make sure layer 46 Milling is included in the profile or outline layer when exporting Gerber files.\n\
<br>\n\
<br>\n\
Alternatively, you can use the built-in Seeed Fusion CAM file. Find it under <i>Third-Party</i> CAM files.\n\
<br>\n\
<br>\n\
This part has an overhanging portion. The edge of the PCB should be aligned with the line marked <i>PCB Edge</i> to be mounted correctly. <br><br>\n\
<b><a href="https://www.seeedstudio.com/opl.html" title="https://www.seeedstudio.com/opl.html">Seeed Fusion PCBA OPL</a><br>\n\
<a href="https://www.seeedstudio.com/fusion_pcb.html">Order PCB/PCBA Now</a><br><br>\n\
<a href="https://www.seeedstudio.com">www.seeedstudio.com</a>\n\
<br></b>';
Value off;
